sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS MethRfc2889ForwardingIterations ('FrameSize' INTEGER, 'Load' FLOAT, 'ILoad' FLOAT, 'OLoad' FLOAT, 'TheoreticalFrameRate' INTERGER, 'FrameForwardingRate' INTEGER, 'FrameLoss' INTEGER, 'TotalFrameCount' INTEGER, 'TxPort' VARCHAR, 'RxPort' VARCHAR)

SELECT Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'FrameSize', Sb.PercentageLoad AS 'Load', ((Sb.MbpsLoad * 100.0 / 8) / Sb.PercentageLoad) As 'ILoad', Sb.MbpsLoad AS 'OLoad', ROUND((Sb.FpsLoad * 100.0) / Sb.PercentageLoad) AS 'TheoreticalFrameRate', ROUND((RxRes.FrameCount)/((LastArrivalTime - FirstArrivalTime) / 1000000.0)) AS 'FrameForwardingRate', DroppedFrameCount AS 'FrameLoss', SigFrameCount + DroppedFrameCount - DuplicateFrameCount AS 'TotalFrameCount', TxRes.PortName AS 'TxPort', RxRes.PortName AS 'RxPort' FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN Streamblock AS Sb ON RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = TxRes.ParentStreamblock AND TxRes.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle

sql_statement.static: INSERT INTO MethRfc2889FrameForwarding(FrameSize, Load, TheoreticalFrameRate, FrameForwardingRate) SELECT MethRfc2889ForwardingIterations.FrameSize, MethRfc2889ForwardingIterations.Load, MethRfc2889ForwardingIterations.TheoreticalFrameRate, MethRfc2889ForwardingIterations.FrameForwardingRate FROM MethRfc2889ForwardingIterations, (SELECT FrameSize, MAX(Load) AS alLoad FROM MethRfc2889ForwardingIterations WHERE FrameLoss = 0 GROUP BY FrameSize) AS A  WHERE A.FrameSize = MethRfc2889ForwardingIterations.FrameSize AND A.alLoad = MethRfc2889ForwardingIterations.Load
INSERT INTO MethRfc2889FrameForwarding SELECT 'Total', 'N/A', SUM(TheoreticalFrameRate), SUM(FrameForwardingRate) from MethRfc2889FrameForwarding
